Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.99,0:12:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行呢\N沒有新運輸計劃的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ也不是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們加強了戒備啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.97,0:12:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我心裡想消滅巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但還要很多時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐你要繼續獨自戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人在哪裡做甚麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只好自己行動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做得到的，你僅管說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我甚麼也會幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚餐妳可以弄牛排給我吃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是，我是認真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這樣已經足夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是甚麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼…鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.48,0:13:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖地跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.86,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗就會當場沒命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨你喜歡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那支雷射砲很強力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這衛星化成飛灰\N也沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊啊   甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.28,0:13:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種地方變成怎樣也和我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想只是做一個技師軍官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能解開這部鋼彈系統之謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫特校的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.75,0:14:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就會成為落後的無用之物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.52,0:14:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的OZ需要新的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.89,0:14:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了那目的，我甚麼事也會做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.86,0:14:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來這裡!鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要的只是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然要我戴上古怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.99,0:14:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想我做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.36,0:14:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這部飛翼零式和MD戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是用實彈啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂\N但我或許會中途逃走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經把飛翼零式改為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能從外面停止機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你有任何異常舉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.15,0:15:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會變成那個衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果在這位置用來福鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星就會有損毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，就那樣戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼看見甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.93,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然也看見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.96,0:15:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛翼零式想讓駕駛員看見甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種東西我怎知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯!我的對手是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼回事…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.99,0:17:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我究竟做過甚麼…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎會的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.52,0:18:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事…人類…怎麼做得到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.26,0:18:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類的意識改革後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.26,0:18:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，在改變潮流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劃時代系統之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒有不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.81,0:18:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特蘭特特尉!你聽到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖地把飛翼零式交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是茲巴洛夫特校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆!把飛翼零式交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.69,0:18:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要消滅他們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止，特蘭特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那系統…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是飛翼零式!它一直飛過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫特校!要俘虜它嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特蘭特這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.93,0:19:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒，還沒能看見一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.43,0:19:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，盡情放馬過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要去!迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那身體狀況不能戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是鋼彈的駕駛員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.25,0:19:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那系統不是人類能駕御的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.95,0:19:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無論如何要制止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不斷擴張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的意識不斷擴張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.94,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還差一點就能看見一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還差一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒，還不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不夠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.64,0:20:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能清楚看見你的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你死去的模樣也能看見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.61,0:20:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連力量也是對方佔優勢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.69,0:20:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋，你還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠力量贏不了我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.77,0:21:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死在這裡\N而我就抓緊榮耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要看過才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有招叫同歸於盡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎會輸給你這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是輸給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是輸給飛翼零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒理由會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不明白嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸，沒理由會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸給區區這種系統…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.30,0:22:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類做不到那種事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有人做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是超越人類的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.71,0:22:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.76,0:22:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.76,0:22:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.76,0:22:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.76,0:23:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.26,0:23:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.76,0:23:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.76,0:23:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.55,0:23:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯再次戴起面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.53,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不斷消滅羅姆斐拉的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.63,0:23:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭這種行動的迪爾麥優候爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,召見莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.77,0:23:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,質問她他是否支援米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.44,0:23:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.54,0:23:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,察知殲滅特列斯派作戰的希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.31,0:23:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自前往最有可能戰死的戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.84,0:23:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第三十三話
